text: Madeleine Jouffroy (born 20 November 1927) is a French gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:Living people Category:French female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Chalon-sur-Saône
